            These core principles guide every decision we make and every solution we create.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 animate-on-scroll group hover:-translate-y-4 hover:rotate-y-6 perspective-1000 transform-gpu">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-300">
              <Lightbulb className="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Innovation</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">
              We constantly push the boundaries of what's possible, embracing new technologies 
              and methodologies to deliver cutting-edge solutions.
            </p>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 animate-on-scroll group hover:-translate-y-4 hover:rotate-y-6 perspective-1000 transform-gpu" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-300">
              <Users className="h-8 w-8 text-secondary-600" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">
              We believe in the power of teamwork, both within our organization and in 
              partnership with our clients to achieve exceptional results.
            </p>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 animate-on-scroll group hover:-translate-y-4 hover:rotate-y-6 perspective-1000 transform-gpu" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all duration-300">
              <Award className="h-8 w-8 text-accent-600" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">
              We are committed to delivering the highest quality solutions, paying attention 
              to every detail and continuously improving our craft.
            </p>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Company History -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="animate-on-scroll">
            <img 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184339/pexels-photo-3184339.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" 
              alt="Team collaboration" 
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
            />
          </div>
          
          <div class="animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
              Our Journey
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                Founded in 2020, KruxxTech began as a small team of passionate developers 
                with a shared vision of creating meaningful technology solutions. What started 
                as a modest consultancy has grown into a comprehensive technology partner 
                for businesses across various industries.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                Over the years, we've had the privilege of working with startups, established 
                enterprises, and everything in between. Each project has taught us something new 
                and helped us refine our approach to building software that truly serves its users.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                Today, we continue to grow and evolve, always staying true to our core mission 
                of creating technology that makes a positive impact in the world.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
